rsections connected by well-labeled bike-friendly…","fields":{"slug":"closing-bike-points"},"frontmatter":{"date":"15 <span> Feb </span>","title":"Closing The BikePoints Project","description":"Ending my work on the BikePoints project.","tags":["bikepoints","bicycling","programming"],"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='62'%20height='62'%20viewBox='0%200%2062%2062'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M4%204L3%2022v17h57V3L32%202C7%202%204%202%204%204m0%2048c0%208%200%209%201%206%201-7%206-12%2013-13s15%206%2015%2014v3h6c6%200%206%200%206-3%200-2%200-2-1-1-1%202-4%203-4%201l3-6%203-6%204%205%203%207c0%202-2%201-4-1-1-1-1-1-1%201%200%203%200%203%206%203h6V41H4v11m8-3c-3%202-6%208-6%2011%200%202%201%202%208%202%206%200%207%200%207-2h-3c-3%200-3%200-3-3%200-4%200-4%204-4l4%201-3%201c-4%200-4%202%200%202%202%200%203%201%203%203%200%203%209%203%209%200%200-10-13-17-20-11'%20fill='%23d3d3d3'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/d59ff/MA_DOT_Sign.png","srcSet":"/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/a86fc/MA_DOT_Sign.png 81w,\n/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/091ba/MA_DOT_Sign.png 163w,\n/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/d59ff/MA_DOT_Sign.png 325w,\n/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/3f5e0/MA_DOT_Sign.png 488w,\n/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/9136b/MA_DOT_Sign.png 650w,\n/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/f8892/MA_DOT_Sign.png 652w","srcWebp":"/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/986c5/MA_DOT_Sign.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/1e7ab/MA_DOT_Sign.webp 81w,\n/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/d450b/MA_DOT_Sign.webp 163w,\n/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/986c5/MA_DOT_Sign.webp 325w,\n/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/ca8ec/MA_DOT_Sign.webp 488w,\n/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/84bc5/MA_DOT_Sign.webp 650w,\n/static/d683d250a5641198c3f3768a8b5dc05b/843bd/MA_DOT_Sign.webp 652w","sizes":"(max-width: 325px) 100vw, 325px"}}}}}},{"node":{"excerpt":"As chill winds descend from the north and leaves turn to yellow and red, fall, and crunch underfoot, I wish we could huddle together, sharing hot drinks and thoughts, and feeling comfort in one another’s presence. Instead, we congregate over Zoom calls and emails, seeking connectedness in the harsh…","fields":{"slug":"2020-october-update"},"frontmatter":{"date":"26 <span> Oct </span>","title":"October Update","description":"As chill winds descend from the north and leaves turn to yellow and red, fall, and crunch underfoot, I wish we could huddle together, sharing hot drinks and thoughts, and feeling comfort in one another’s' presence. Instead, we congregate over Zoom calls and emails, seeking connectedness in the harsh cold glares of our computer screens. So I'm emailing you again; to tell you about my last few months; to try to keep the interpersonal connections that I have; to try and grow the connections that I don't have; and to connect with you in whatever way is available to me.","tags":["accountability"],"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='62'%20height='62'%20viewBox='0%200%2062%2062'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M27%208C17%209%208%2015%204%2024c-3%206-3%206%2013%2010l14%204-13%208-13%208%204%204%203%204h38l3-3C73%2039%2056%204%2027%208'%20fill='%23d3d3d3'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/b74b8a43cb94a0e56b84905fadd21c24/d59ff/pie-chart.png","srcSet":"/static/b74b8a43cb94a0e56b84905fadd21c24/a86fc/pie-chart.png 81w,\n/static/b74b8a43cb94a0e56b84905fadd21c24/091ba/pie-chart.png 163w,\n/static/b74b8a43cb94a0e56b84905fadd21c24/d59ff/pie-chart.png 325w,\n/static/b74b8a43cb94a0e56b84905fadd21c24/3f5e0/pie-chart.png 488w,\n/static/b74b8a43cb94a0e56b84905fadd21c24/9136b/pie-chart.png 650w,\n/static/b74b8a43cb9